@AgencyAssetAPI_HostAddress = http://localhost:5262
@ApiKey = your-local-dev-api-key

### Health (no API key)
GET {{AgencyAssetAPI_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Demo — all assets (no API key)
GET {{AgencyAssetAPI_HostAddress}}/api/demo?maxDays=90
Accept: application/json

### Demo — non-audited assets (no API key)
GET {{AgencyAssetAPI_HostAddress}}/api/demo/non-audited?maxDays=90
Accept: application/json

### Demo — mark asset audited (no API key)
PUT {{AgencyAssetAPI_HostAddress}}/api/demo/1/audit
Accept: application/json

### Demo — reset seed data (no API key)
POST {{AgencyAssetAPI_HostAddress}}/api/demo/reset
Accept: application/json

### Secured — all assets
GET {{AgencyAssetAPI_HostAddress}}/api/assets
Accept: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}

### Secured — non-audited assets
GET {{AgencyAssetAPI_HostAddress}}/api/assets/non-audited?maxDays=90
Accept: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}

### Secured — update audit date
PUT {{AgencyAssetAPI_HostAddress}}/api/assets/1/audit
Accept: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
